{"tid":221440,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"英文被屌打.....","createTime":"2017-04-28T16:53:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T03:05:11.000Z","uid":103708,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"41a69fc74cf2fdeeb746d941140e0dfb3021157c","tid":221440,"uid":103708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:53:11.000Z","msg":"由細細個開始已經好怕英文，考試測驗個D好多時都唔合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但一直無理，得過且過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搞到而家個英文底好差，會成日講錯字（明明個字唔係咁解）搞到無乜自信心講英文<br />\n<br />\n之前都由佢唔理，但係近排因為種種問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 令我好想正視呢個問題，好想威番次比人睇，好想令自己學好呢種語言，但永遠三分鐘熱度，所以懇求各位巴打點樣可以學好英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e39287b5a9b01b321e723f4b0965cadab6c43e4","tid":221440,"uid":93266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:56:59.000Z","msg":"日日都用英文作文..<br />\n<br />\n作完之後再讀返出黎.."},{"pid":"ee54625aa959443c0e4f336a989ebdfe85482cd4","tid":221440,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:58:38.000Z","msg":"打篇文上黎睇睇先"},{"pid":"a313c3745a67e7d88be1c9127a3c3f882129c781","tid":221440,"uid":107971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:59:39.000Z","msg":"語言呢d野如果自己冇興趣冇動力去學，其他人真係好難幫到<br />\n<br />\n如果真係有心學的話建議由聽英文歌入手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：英文文盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd8b49947b9b7a56b5254a29ff67e8308932792","tid":221440,"uid":103708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:08:34.000Z","msg":"其實我主要想練聽講能力，所以想從煲英美劇/聽歌入手，想係呢方面培養左興趣先<br />\n<br />\n同埋我好鐘意睇一個外國Youtuber叫Casey，但係一定要有中字先明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試過就咁睇佢d片加youtube d 英文字幕，只有2-3成明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以目標係想培養左興趣再逐步黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106fed572ae39f9ca01e0e8519583d3ab614c580","tid":221440,"uid":86403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:09:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由細細個開始已經好怕英文，考試測驗個D好多時都唔合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但一直無理，得過且過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搞到而家個英文底好差，會成日講錯字（明明個字唔係咁解）搞到無乜自信心講英文<br />\n<br />\n之前都由佢唔理，但係近排因為種種問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 令我好想正視呢個問題，好想威番次比人睇，好想令自己學好呢種語言，但永遠三分鐘熱度，所以懇求各位巴打點樣可以學好英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n慢慢增加接觸英文既時間，真係要堅持，去到咁上下變習慣，聽同睇多d先<br />\n吸收多d先，先再試下用出黎。<br />\n我都係邁向緊呢個目標既一員<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之搵個令你提起興趣，去接觸多d英文既方法。 <br />\n最後，要唔怕7。<br />\n激戰:怯你就輸一世。<br />\n怯你就成世都唔識，有咩好驚。<br />\n雖然我成日都好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實你早d學好，咪早d可以用囉。"},{"pid":"b70f14c9a9bbf65cc02081ed3da7415c377b3121","tid":221440,"uid":57675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:09:41.000Z","msg":"睇美劇<br />\n有啲網有晒中英雙語字幕<br />\nJ女主角又好 J埋男主角都好<br />\n揀返三五七套鐘意嘅黎煲下點都有進步"},{"pid":"cbee4cdadd83be70fe6d4a2b935e6fa6b6e64d49","tid":221440,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:10:22.000Z","msg":"屌咩打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇怕你中文都唔撚合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9dca6834bf76ef2020f5d5d78b6309d3a9f91c5","tid":221440,"uid":93266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:12:21.000Z","msg":"哦 , 咁你有主意既咪煲下劇先囉...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過絕多數人學英